```
package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"regexp"
)

func main() {
	first := "abc"
	second := "xyz"
	sampleRegex := regexp.MustCompile(first + second)

	match := sampleRegex.Match([]byte("abcxyz"))
	fmt.Println(match)

	match = sampleRegex.Match([]byte("abc"))
	fmt.Println(match)

	match = sampleRegex.Match([]byte("xyz"))
	fmt.Println(match)

	match = sampleRegex.Match([]byte("abd"))
	fmt.Println(match)
}
```

```
package main

import (
    "fmt"
    "regexp"
)
func main() {
    first := "abc"
    second := "xyz"
    third := "123"
    sampleRegex := regexp.MustCompile(first + second + third)

    match := sampleRegex.Match([]byte("abcxyz123"))
    fmt.Println(match)

    match = sampleRegex.Match([]byte("abc"))
    fmt.Println(match)

    match = sampleRegex.Match([]byte("xyz"))
    fmt.Println(match)

    match = sampleRegex.Match([]byte("abcxyz"))
    fmt.Println(match)

    match = sampleRegex.Match([]byte("abd"))
    fmt.Println(match)
}
```
